<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Error</title>
  <style>
    body {
      background-color: #f8f9fa;
      font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
      text-align: center;
      padding: 2rem;
    }

    h1 {
      font-size: 3rem;
      margin-bottom: 1rem;
    }

    p {
      font-size: 1.5rem;
      margin-bottom: 2rem;
    }

    button {
      font-size: 1.5rem;
      padding: 1rem 2rem;
      border-radius: 0.5rem;
      background-color: #007bff;
      color: #fff;
      border: none;
      cursor: pointer;
      transition: all 0.3s ease;
    }

    button:hover {
      background-color: #0069d9;
    }

    @media (max-width: 576px) {
      h1 {
        font-size: 2rem;
      }

      p {
        font-size: 1rem;
      }

      button {
        font-size: 1rem;
        padding: 0.5rem 1rem;
      }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <h1>Oh oh!</h1>
  <p>Something went wrong. We're sorry, there seems to be an error. Please try again later.</p>
